</inertial>

This defines mass and how the object moves.
	â€¢	mass value="0" â†’ static object (doesnâ€™t fall or move)
	â€¢	If you set it to something > 0 (like mass="5"), it becomes a dynamic body that reacts to gravity and forces.

If youâ€™re building walls, platforms, or the ground: use mass="0".

